## WHAT EACH CONFIG DOES

| Config Key | Purpose | When Used |
|-----------|---------|-----------|
| `DefaultConnection` | Orthopedic DB location | Always - local data |
| `ExternalPatientCache` | Redis for UUID caching | Patient lookups |
| `PhysiotherapyApi.BaseUrl` | Where Physio system is | Publishing/calling Physio |
| `PhysiotherapyApi.RetryAttempts` | How many times to retry | If Physio API fails |
| `MessageBroker.ConnectionString` | RabbitMQ location | Event pub/sub |
| `CircuitBreaker.FailureThreshold` | When to stop trying | High failure rate |
| `ExternalPatientIds.Enabled` | Generate UUIDs | Patient creation |

